---
// Components
// - Layout
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro'
import Row from '../components/ui/Row.astro'
import Col from '../components/ui/Col.astro'
// - Blocks
import Hero from '../components/blocks/hero/SimpleHeroNeutral.astro'
import SectionSticky from '../components/blocks/basic/StickySidebarTransparent.astro'
// - UI
import Header from '../components/ui/Header.astro'

// Content
// - SEO
const SEO = {
	title: 'PromptMarketing | Terms & Conditions',
	description:
		'Review the terms and conditions for using PromptMarketing services, including service agreements and policies.'
}
// - Hero
const heroData = {
	title: 'Clear and  Fair Use of Our Services',
	subtitle: 'Terms & Conditions',
	text: 'Welcome to our platform. These Terms and Conditions outline the rules, responsibilities, and limitations that apply when using our product. Please read them carefully, as by continuing to use our services, you agree to comply with them.'
}
---

<Layout title={SEO.title} description={SEO.description}>
	<Hero
		title={heroData.title}
		subtitle={heroData.subtitle}
		text={heroData.text}
		textClasses="max-w-xl!"
	/>
	<SectionSticky>
		<Header
			title="About This Agreement"
			subtitle="Introduction"
			headingLevel="h2"
			titleClasses="bg-white dark:bg-neutral-950"
			slot="sidebar"
		/>
		<Row decorationBorder="top bottom" decorationBorderStyle="dashed" style="transparent">
			<Col span="12" style="transparent">
				<div class="text-basic bg-white p-8 dark:bg-neutral-950 [&_h3]:text-xl!">
					<h3>Welcome to PromptMarketing</h3>
					<p>
						Welcome to PromptMarketing! We’re excited to have you here. Our platform is designed to help
						you launch, manage, and scale your product with clarity and confidence. By using PromptMarketing, you agree to these Terms and Conditions, so please take a moment to read them
						carefully.
					</p>
					<p>
						Your satisfaction matters to us. If you have any questions or concerns about these
						terms, please reach out. Our team is here to support you and ensure that your experience
						with PromptMarketing is both seamless and rewarding.
					</p>
					<h3>Acceptance of Terms</h3>
					<p>
						By accessing or using our services, you agree to comply with and be bound by these Terms
						of Service as well as our Privacy Policy. If you do not agree with any part of these
						terms, you may not use our services. Your continued use of PromptMarketing constitutes
						acceptance of these terms.
					</p>
					<p>
						We may update these terms from time to time. Any changes will be posted on our website,
						and it is your responsibility to review them periodically. Continued use of the service
						after changes have been published indicates your acceptance of the revised terms.
					</p>
					<h3>Our Commitment to You</h3>
					<p>
						At PromptMarketing, we are committed to delivering reliable and high-quality services. Our
						mission is to help you bring your ideas to life and create meaningful impact through
						streamlined workflows and innovative tools. We continually work to improve our platform
						so that you always have the best possible experience.
					</p>
					<p>
						We value your feedback and suggestions. Please don’t hesitate to share your thoughts on
						how we can improve. Your input helps us enhance PromptMarketing and shape it into a platform
						that grows with your needs.
					</p>
				</div>
			</Col>
		</Row>
	</SectionSticky>
	<SectionSticky>
		<Header
			title="Registration and Use"
			subtitle="User Accounts"
			headingLevel="h2"
			titleClasses="bg-white dark:bg-neutral-950"
			slot="sidebar"
		/>
		<Row decorationBorder="top bottom" decorationBorderStyle="dashed" style="transparent">
			<Col span="12" style="transparent">
				<div class="text-basic bg-white p-8 dark:bg-neutral-950 [&_h3]:text-xl!">
					<h3>Registration</h3>
					<p>
						To access certain features of PromptMarketing, you will need to create a user account. During
						registration, you must provide accurate and complete information. This ensures that we
						can deliver the best possible service and maintain the security and proper functionality
						of your account.
					</p>
					<p>
						By registering, you also agree to keep your details up to date. Providing false or
						outdated information may affect your access to specific features of PromptMarketing or result
						in limitations on your account.
					</p>
					<h3>Account Security</h3>
					<p>
						You are solely responsible for maintaining the confidentiality and security of your
						account. Do not share your password with others, and notify us immediately if you
						suspect any unauthorized access or use of your account.
					</p>
					<p>
						For enhanced protection, we recommend using a strong, unique password for your PromptMarketing account and enabling two-factor authentication when available. Regularly updating
						your password further reduces the risk of unauthorized access.
					</p>
					<h3>Account Usage</h3>
					<p>
						As the account holder, you are responsible for all activities carried out under your
						account. This includes any actions performed by individuals who may have gained access
						to it. Please ensure your account is used responsibly and in accordance with these
						Terms.
					</p>
					<p>
						If we detect suspicious or unauthorized activity, we may take protective measures, which
						could include temporarily suspending access, requesting additional verification, or
						other actions necessary to secure your information. Our priority is to safeguard your
						account and data.
					</p>
				</div>
			</Col>
		</Row>
	</SectionSticky>
	<SectionSticky>
		<Header
			title="General Restrictions and Liability"
			subtitle="Limitations and Liability"
			headingLevel="h2"
			titleClasses="bg-white dark:bg-neutral-950"
			slot="sidebar"
		/>
		<Row decorationBorder="top bottom" decorationBorderStyle="dashed" style="transparent">
			<Col span="12" style="transparent">
				<div class="text-basic bg-white p-8 dark:bg-neutral-950 [&_h3]:text-xl!">
					<h3>General Limitations</h3>
					<p>
						PromptMarketing is provided on an “as is” and “as available” basis. We do not warrant that
						the service will be uninterrupted, error-free, or fully secure. All warranties—express
						or implied—are disclaimed, including, but not limited to, implied warranties of
						merchantability, fitness for a particular purpose, and non-infringement.
					</p>
					<p>
						We are not liable for damages arising from the use or inability to use our services,
						including but not limited to direct, indirect, incidental, special, consequential, or
						punitive damages. This includes, without limitation, loss of profits, data, or other
						intangible assets.
					</p>
					<h3>Third-Party Services</h3>
					<p>
						PromptMarketing may include links to third-party websites or services that are not owned or
						controlled by us. We do not endorse, warrant, or assume responsibility for any such
						third-party content, materials, products, or services. Accessing and using these
						services is solely at your own risk.
					</p>
					<p>
						We are not liable for any loss or damage resulting from your interactions with
						third-party websites or services, including the sharing of your personal information.
						You are responsible for reviewing the terms and privacy policies of any third-party
						services you choose to use.
					</p>
					<h3>Maximum Liability</h3>
					<p>
						In no event shall our total liability to you, for all claims arising out of or relating
						to the use or inability to use PromptMarketing, exceed the amount paid by you, if any, for
						accessing PromptMarketing during the twelve (12) months immediately preceding the date of the
						claim. This limitation applies regardless of the nature of the claim—whether based in
						contract, warranty, tort, or otherwise.
					</p>
					<p>
						Some jurisdictions do not allow the exclusion or limitation of liability for
						consequential or incidental damages. In such cases, our liability will be limited to the
						maximum extent permitted under applicable law.
					</p>
				</div>
			</Col>
		</Row>
	</SectionSticky>
</Layout>
